Junior Golfer Special
spamber
June 12, 2025
Summertime is for everyone!
At Village Green we’re inviting the whole family to join in on the fun with a special promotion. All summer, junior golfers can play for FREE with a paid adult (excludes cart fees).
From now until August 31st, any golfer under 15 years old gets complimentary greens fees when they bring in a paying adult. So grab the kiddos and make it a family fun day at Village Green Golf Club!
Book your tee time today!

June 12, 2025
Spend your Thursdays on the green while saving green with our incredible summer special.
Village Green Golf Club is the place to be this summer and even more so on Thursdays
This summer you can play 18 holes for only $25!
Every Thursday from 7 am to 11 am you can take advantage of this amazing deal
Don’t miss out,
book your tee time
today!
Or call us at (941) 922-9500

Summer Memberships
spamber
June 9, 2025
Summer is here and so are our Summer Memberships!
Take advantage of our seasonal pricing so you can get the most golf in this summer.
From May 1st – October 31st you can purchase and use your summer membership to get the most bang for your buck.
What’s even better is that memberships also include discounted cart fees and 25% off food and beverages! Take a look at our pricing and see which membership works best for you:
Single – $425
Family – $725
Junior – $249 (15 years and younger)
Stop by for your membership today!
